message: Hello Bob, I have a great product that I think you'll love. I'm willing to let it go for $120.
Thank you for offering the product, Alice. I appreciate it, but I can only pay up to $100 for it.
I understand you're looking to save some money, Bob. I'm willing to meet you halfway, but I need to make a profit. I can do $110, but that's as low as I can go.
